data.description: Explore the convenience of this superbly located haven in the heart of beachside. Assumable Mortage Available. A 3-bed, 2-bath concrete block residence with a spacious garage and an EXPANSIVE yard, nestled between the Halifax River and Atlantic Ocean awaits you. This property's location seamlessly merges comfort with coastal convenience. Step into a generous living space that effortlessly connects to an inviting dining room that is directly attached to an updated kitchen. Modernize, newly tiled floors and fresh paint, create an unparalleled contemporary ambiance. Indulge in weekends in the expansive yard after family beach moments just minutes away. Restaurants, shopping, the beach, and The Casements are within a mile from home. All information is deemed accurate but not guaranteed.
